{"tid":1226141,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢要有所準備 少許油麻地五金鋪指南","createTime":"2019-06-15T10:04:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T03:38:32.000Z","uid":72138,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d573498df87f8897e4f634e57e7f5ed4532505a9","tid":1226141,"uid":72138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T10:04:19.000Z","msg":"是咁的，今日下午五點個陣同朋友發夢去左油麻地，<br />\n行左幾間五金鋪，搵豬嘴口罩 3M 3200A，夢入面我地格左價。<br />\n<br />\n上海街 <br />\n權益五金漆油 180蚊 大約有20個<br />\n錦威五金 120蚊 8至9個<br />\n<br />\n新鎮地街 <br />\n明生五金 無<br />\n<br />\n廣東道 997至991號<br />\n有發五金漆油 98蚊 無曬貨 可以落訂 星期一會翻貨<br />\n如果唔落訂 佢星期一本身都會翻貨 10個 8個<br />\n炭芯補充裝 49蚊 一個<br />\n10個而上的話 口罩95 芯47<br />\n<br />\n廣東道 952號 <br />\n創紀梯具公司 82蚊 <br />\nDr Safety 手套 員工話同3M 差不多 10蚊<br />\n如果買棉芯 一set 10塊 70蚊 棉芯會隔得快啲<br />\n<br />\n個夢好長 歡迎大家補充我個夢"},{"pid":"6683fa11876166897a023cf6aade72f426565df2","tid":1226141,"uid":149041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T10:56:04.000Z","msg":"上海街嗰間算唔算係坐地起價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9410e6bebda12c10886ae322deb32231a1a44e8","tid":1226141,"uid":72138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6683fa11876166897a023cf6aade72f426565df2","tid":1226141,"uid":149041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T10:56:04.000Z","msg":"上海街嗰間算唔算係坐地起價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:09:20.000Z","msg":"食人血饅頭"},{"pid":"cef337dec383948db5a4d823a9c30e43576b4a5f","tid":1226141,"uid":72138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:18:07.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"364f6546e1884d790fba6ed33057d24b04559e39","tid":1226141,"uid":25164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:38:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\"